* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 18-Mar-25 18:29 Page   1
*                                      EXERC8.CBL
* Options: LIST(EXERC8.LST) ASMLIST(EXERC8.GRP)
     1 IDENTIFICATION  DIVISION.
     2 PROGRAM-ID.     EXERC8.
     3 AUTHOR.         YHAGO PESSOA.
     4 INSTALLATION.   FATEC-SP.
     5 DATE-WRITTEN.   18/03/2025.
     6 DATE-COMPILED. 18-Mar-25 18:29.
     7 SECURITY. APENAS O AUTOR PODE MODIFICA-LO.
     8
     9 ENVIRONMENT     DIVISION.
    10 CONFIGURATION SECTION.
    11 SOURCE-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    12 OBJECT-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    13 SPECIAL-NAMES.    DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    14
    15 INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
    16 FILE-CONTROL.
    17     SELECT   CADFUN        ASSIGN      TO       DISK
    18     ORGANIZATION  IS         LINE        SEQUENTIAL.
    19     SELECT   CADSAI        ASSIGN     TO       DISK
    20     ORGANIZATION  IS         LINE        SEQUENTIAL.
    21
    22 DATA           DIVISION.
    23 FILE SECTION.
    24
    25 FD  CADFUN
    26     LABEL   RECORD  STANDARD
    27     VALUE    OF FILE-ID    IS          "CADALU.DAT".
    28 01  REG-ENT.
    29     02 NUM-ENT           PIC 9(05).
    30     02 NOME-ENT          PIC X(20).
    31     02 SAL-ENT           PIC 9(05)V99.
    32
    33 FD  CADSAI
    34     LABEL   RECORD  STANDARD
    35     VALUE   OF FILE-ID    IS   "CADSAI.DAT".
    36 01  REG-SAI.
    37     02 NUM-SAI           PIC 9(05).
    38     02 NOME-SAI          PIC X(20).
    39     02 SAL-SAI           PIC 9(05)V99.
    40
    41 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    42     77 FIM-ARQ          PIC X(03)    VALUE "NAO".
    43     77 SAL-CONT         PIC 9(05)V99.
    44
    45
    46 PROCEDURE        DIVISION.
    47
    48 EXEMPLO.
    49     PERFORM INICIO.
    50     PERFORM PRINCIPAL
    51       UNTIL FIM-ARQ EQUAL "SIM".
    52     PERFORM TERMINO
    53     STOP RUN.
    54 INICIO.
    55     OPEN INPUT CADFUN
    56          OUTPUT CADSAI.
    57     PERFORM LEITURA.
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 18-Mar-25 18:29 Page   2
*                                      EXERC8.CBL
    58
    59     LEITURA.
    60         READ CADFUN
    61            AT END
    62            MOVE "SIM" TO FIM-ARQ.
    63 PRINCIPAL.
    64     PERFORM GRAVACAO.
    65     PERFORM LEITURA.
    66
    67     GRAVACAO.
    68         IF SAL-ENT <= 1000
    69             COMPUTE SAL-CONT = SAL-ENT * (112/100)
    70         ELSE IF SAL-ENT <= 2000
    71             COMPUTE SAL-CONT = SAL-ENT * (111/100)
    72         ELSE
    73             COMPUTE SAL-CONT= SAL-ENT * (110/100)
    74         END-IF.
    75         MOVE NUM-ENT TO NUM-SAI
    76         MOVE NOME-ENT TO NOME-SAI
    77         MOVE SAL-CONT TO SAL-SAI
    78         WRITE REG-SAI.
    79
    80 TERMINO.
    81     CLOSE CADFUN
    82           CADSAI.
